$ CSS: @media (… aspect-ratio: )

Change the background color depending of the *width to height* ratio of the media's viewport:
code {
<style>

 → development/web/CSS/selectors/at-rules/media (min-aspect-ratio: 3/2) { body { background-color: lightblue ; } } /* Wider than aspect ratio  */
 → development/web/CSS/selectors/at-rules/media (max-aspect-ratio: 3/2) { body { background-color: lightcoral; } } /* Taller than aspect ratio */

</style>
code }
